ELDER walked out of the shuttle and looked down at TALON a smile on
his beastial face. He placed his hands on his hips, looking for a
moment more like a warrior then the councellor he has been all this
time.

"Do you need to go to the medical bay?" He said as he held out his
hand to help her up if she needed it.
